#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:6
msgid "なぜ cymel ?"
msgstr "Why cymel?"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:8
msgid "以下に挙げるのが cymel のゴールです。"
msgstr "The following are the goals of cymel."

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:10
msgid "MEL よりもオブジェクト指向に！"
msgstr "More object-oriented than MEL!"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:11
msgid "API よりも手軽に！"
msgstr "Easier than API!"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:12
msgid "PyMEL よりも軽量で軽快に！"
msgstr "Lighter and more nimble than PyMEL!"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:14
msgid ""
"Maya のスクリプティングをより Python らしくすることは pymel で達成されました （その必要性は `Why PyMEL?`__ "
"に書かれています）。"
msgstr ""
"Making Maya scripting more Python-like was accomplished with pymel (the need"
" for it is described in `Why PyMEL?`__)."

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:19
msgid "その点をリスペクトした上で、 pymel の問題を解決し、便利な機能をより軽快に実現します。"
msgstr ""
"Respecting this point, we will solve the problems of pymel and implement "
"useful functions more easily."

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:22
msgid "もっと快適な Python スクリプティングを"
msgstr "More comfortable Python scripting"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:24
msgid "とにかく軽量で軽快に"
msgstr "Anyway, lightweight and nimble"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:25
msgid "高速に（C++ 実装が完了すればもっと高速に）"
msgstr "Fast (even faster once the C++ implementation is complete)"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:26
msgid "数学クラスには、リギングなどで便利な機能を充実"
msgstr ""
"Mathematics classes are equipped with useful functions such as rigging."

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:28
msgid "信頼性高く、お行儀よく"
msgstr "Reliable and well behaved"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:30
msgid "全ての変更操作が undo 可能であることを保証"
msgstr "Guarantees that all changes are undoable"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:31
msgid "Maya の設定を書き換えない"
msgstr "Do not rewrite Maya settings"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:32
msgid "scriptJob や MMessage などのコールバックを埋め込まない"
msgstr "Do not embed callbacks such as scriptJob or MMessage"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:33
msgid "Networked Plug を保持しない設計"
msgstr "Designed to not hold networked plugs"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:34
msgid "インスタンス番号に依存するプラグを保持しないことの推奨"
msgstr "Recommendation not to maintain plugs that depend on instance numbers"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:36
msgid "全てをラップすることは目指さない"
msgstr "I don't aim to wrap everything"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:38
msgid "コンポーネントはサポートしない"
msgstr "does not support components"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:39
msgid "コマンドはラップしない"
msgstr "commands do not wrap"

#: ../srcs/whycymel.rst:40
msgid "多くのクラスに API やコマンド相当の機能をつけるなどの多機能を目指さない"
msgstr ""
"Do not aim for multi-functionality such as adding functions equivalent to "
"API or commands to many classes."
